{"tid":1923972,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"請各DSE考生入一入黎","createTime":"2020-03-13T11:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T14:40:42.000Z","uid":176272,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"41ee1acb31b0be1f0c3a90543e3899e2c71611b7","tid":1923972,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"叫得你入黎，梗係有嘢提你啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢排DSE時期 學店又出沒啦</span><br />\n<br />\n啱啱就收到個扮做問卷嘅電話，<br />\n但實質聽得出係sall課程電話，請求各位，<br />\n如果遇到此情況，請唔好猶豫，唔好同情佢唔好心軟，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大大力cut佢電話cut完仲要封鎖，</span></span></strong>封鎖完，佢會轉number 再call多次，請再cut多次<br />\n<br />\n佢地用盡一切方法，扮到好關心你，講到你唔讀佢地課程，人生就冇希望咁，請你千萬不要心軟，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋會扮同你做測試，引你去佢地公司，入得去，你都幾難出得返黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己諗吓，唔伏嘅話，點會要電話call你r生意呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前DSE考生的忠告"},{"pid":"4a42117db2bc1b38fe56663975009628562d3199","tid":1923972,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac50376da783994c00940c7a1bacae3c4cfad23","tid":1923972,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:36:19.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"99cf8af3c6a89b51fa38e60bcdc88009f67a8cf5","tid":1923972,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"64360d428ec8acfbe3c87bf0092fa6cf181368ee","tid":1923972,"uid":78222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"仲有 無5科2係讀唔到高級文憑架<br />\n無5科2都讀得嘅係用黎呃無知婦孺"},{"pid":"06f0d814a7c89e07783b47b5e5a69fea1ac24ec1","tid":1923972,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a